13 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Rams\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Cardinals\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=[[State Farm Stadium]], [[Glendale, Arizona]]\n|attendance=\n|weather={{tooltip|TBD|To be determined}} ([[retractable roof]] stadium)\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: at San Francisco 49ers====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Los Angeles Rams at San Francisco 49ers&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Rams\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=49ers\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=[[Levi's Stadium]], [[Santa Clara, California]]\n|attendance=\n|weather=\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: at Seattle Seahawks====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Los Angeles Rams at Seattle Seahawks&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Rams\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Seahawks\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=[[CenturyLink Field]], [[Seattle, Washington]]\n|attendance=\n|weather=\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: at Philadelphia Eagles====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Los Angeles Rams at Philadelphia Eagles&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Rams\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Eagles\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=[[Lincoln Financial Field]], [[Philadelphia, Pennsylvania]]\n|attendance=\n|weather=\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: at Washington Redskins====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Los Angeles Rams|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Los